Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.92,0:02:14.06,opcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}比魔法还要强大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.63,0:02:20.07,opcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}我觉得那是无人所能取代的你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.27,0:02:25.36,opcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}这份Power of Love
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.11,0:02:28.70,opcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}因此 I'll be there for you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.90,0:02:31.34,opcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}我相信着这份羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.49,0:02:36.88,opcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}你的空虚 你的唇 你那倔强的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.41,0:02:39.97,opcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}我喜欢 Always I Love you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.15,0:02:42.59,opcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}你我一定可以
