Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.34,0:02:54.81,opcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}到那崭新的世界Go with me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.21,0:01:32.15,opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}I'll be there for you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.39,0:01:34.90,opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}羽ばたいてゆくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.10,0:01:41.32,opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}新しい世界へGo with me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.31,0:01:49.86,opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}手と手をつないで進めば
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.02,0:01:52.63,opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}闇さえ怖れず行けるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.91,0:01:57.38,opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}誰もまだ知らないあの場所へ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.54,0:02:01.13,opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}途中で嵐に遭っても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.33,0:02:03.97,opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}見守る瞳の明かりが
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.16,0:02:08.06,opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}立ち向かう勇気をくれる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.92,0:02:14.06,opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}魔法より強いチカラさ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.63,0:02:20.07,opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}かけがえのないキミを想う
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.27,0:02:25.36,opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}このPower of Love
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.11,0:02:28.70,opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}だからI'll be there for you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.90,0:02:31.34,opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}絆を信じて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.49,0:02:36.88,opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}寂しさも クチビルも 強気なまなざしも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.41,0:02:39.97,opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}好きさ Always I Love you
